sentences: Julia Kadel (born 1986 in Berlin-Kreuzberg) is a German jazz pianist and composer.
She studied psychology at Humboldt University of Berlin, then went on to study jazz piano at the Hochschule für Musik Carl Maria von Weber in Dresden from 2009 to 2014.
In 2014, their debut album Im Vertrauen was released by Blue Note Records/Universal.
It was presented at the Überjazz Festival in Hamburg, and was awarded the first jazz prize from Hochschule für Musik Saar in 2013.
